{"id":"0377c479-8b20-4ec4-baee-d47c4e1ab31d","name":"Galactic Domain","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The galaxy has no <span style=\"color: rgb(177, 18, 38);\"><strong>heroes</strong></span>—only <span style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10);\"><strong>winners</strong></span>.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">In this narrative <span style=\"color: rgb(91, 42, 134);\"><strong>interstellar strategy</strong></span> game, you control not one character, but an <span style=\"color: rgb(177, 18, 38);\"><strong>entire civilization</strong></span>. Whether human or alien, lead your race to <span style=\"color: rgb(212, 175, 55);\"><strong>glory</strong></span>, total domination, or a fragile galactic peace.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Wage war against rival species, forge diplomatic <span style=\"color: rgb(91, 42, 134);\"><strong>alliances</strong></span> worthy of a space UN, manipulate treaties, betray allies, or unify the galaxy under your <span style=\"color: rgb(177, 18, 38);\"><strong>banner</strong></span>. Every decision shapes the balance of <span style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10);\"><strong>power</strong></span>, and no choice comes without consequences.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Here, the galaxy is <span style=\"color: rgb(91, 42, 134);\"><strong>alive</strong></span>, <span style=\"color: rgb(177, 18, 38);\"><strong>reactive</strong></span>, and <span style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10);\"><strong>unforgiving</strong></span>.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">You choose the <span style=\"color: rgb(212, 175, 55);\"><strong>path</strong></span>.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The universe <span style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10);\"><strong>responds</strong></span>.</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"-wLJOMRM02LXvP5EHOr9j.webp","creator":"Rakrak-1.0","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📜 Politics","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":106,"messages":706,"created_at":"2026-01-10T03:58:17.460594+00:00"}